  <h1>Org Design &amp; M&amp;A Integration</h1>
  <p class="project-summary">Following Microsoft's acquisition of Activision Blizzard, our EMEA Go-to-Market organisation — a team of roughly 250 — was asked to reduce headcount by 60 roles as part of wider efficiency goals across the gaming business. I was at the centre of the people side of this transformation: co-designing the future organisation with our MD, planning and executing the reduction with dignity, and helping the remaining team rediscover its footing.</p>

